song.title: Magnetic Charcoal
song.info: Begun as a coop project together with Gustav. At the end of our session we said: "This is not as good as it should be, lets put it on the shelf..." I added: "Sure. Well, atleast now i have something to work on, should i get a flow." On work 3 weeks later i cooked, cleaned, washed, served food for about 30 people, breakfast, lunch and dinner whilst also bringing my laptop beating the sense out of the musical part of my brain. About 90% of the song was made that day. When i woke up, i went to work. When i came home, i went to bed. A good day, all in all.
